OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain moves
OL,6,Fsoutheastwards this evening, clearing
OL,7,Fout to the North Sea by the early
OL,8,Fhours. Later it turns colder and windy
OL,9,Fwith clear spells and showers,
OL,10,Fheaviest in the north and west, with
OL,11,Fhill snow in northern areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FSunny spells and blustery
OL,14,Fwintry showers. The showers most
OL,15,Ffrequent across the north and
OL,16,Fnorthwest where they will be heavy
OL,17,Fwith hail and thunder. Feeling cold
OL,18,Fwith brisk winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
